---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About — simpleBudget" description="The story behind simpleBudget and why we built it.">
  <section class="about-hero">
    <h1>Built for people who hate budgeting</h1>
    <p class="about-sub">
      Most budgeting apps are either too complex or too rigid. We built simpleBudget because we wanted something that takes 2 minutes to set up and stays out of your way the rest of the month.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="values">
    <div class="value-card">
      <h3>Simple by design</h3>
      <p>Every feature earns its place. If it adds complexity without clear value, it doesn't ship. Your budget should be a tool, not a project.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="value-card">
      <h3>Privacy first</h3>
      <p>We don't sell data, run ads, or partner with financial institutions. Your money info stays between you and your budget.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="value-card">
      <h3>Works offline</h3>
      <p>As a PWA, simpleBudget works even when your connection doesn't. Log a transaction on the subway and it syncs when you're back online.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="story">
    <h2>The short version</h2>
    <p>
      simpleBudget started as a personal project — a weekend build to replace a spreadsheet that had gotten out of hand. Turns out a lot of people had the same spreadsheet problem.
    </p>
    <p>
      Today it's used by thousands of people who want to know where their money goes without spending an hour a week on it. We keep it lean, fast, and focused.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <h2>Try it yourself</h2>
    <p>Free to start, no credit card required.</p>
    <a href="https://app.simplebudget.com/signup" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Create Your Budget</a>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .about-hero {
    padding: 5rem 0 3rem;
    max-width: 700px;
  }

  .about-hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .about-sub {
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .values {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    padding: 3rem 0;
  }

  .value-card {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .value-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .value-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .story {
    padding: 3rem 0;
    max-width: 650px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
  }

  .story h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .story p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-section {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 5rem 0;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .cta-section h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .cta-section p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
</style>
